            As O&G Digital Senior Staff Analytics Advocate located at the Oil & Gas Technology Center (OGTC) in Oklahoma City you will work with the O&G Digital team and the OGTC Digital Leader to drive the development, adoption and usage of industrial analytics.  You will work with customers to understand product needs, and with engineers, data scientists and developers to create technical specifications for analytic prototypes to be integrated into products that address the customer requirements.
